{"tid":1482714,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"遇雨則吉","createTime":"2019-08-18T07:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T08:02:24.000Z","uid":62011,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d4ac53747d5d7ddd3c64444180643eb51b6142","tid":1482714,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"遇雨則吉，下雨代表陰陽調和，事情有結果，因此遇雨則吉。《象》曰：「遇雨之吉，群疑亡也。」上九爻裡，遇到許多奇奇怪怪的事情，讓人心中困惑不解，疑雲滿天。遇雨，又代表事情明朗，所有的疑惑一下子全都解開了，所以為吉。"},{"pid":"cdd0993b3d51069e488b2324ffb0f6eb0161ff2a","tid":1482714,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b707a5f5c1ba533893e230c36d37f969237d5dfe","tid":1482714,"uid":245909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"唔好迷信啦"},{"pid":"bd4af4199a0380d666e19cd36da587fc9bf22715","tid":1482714,"uid":290549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6d4ac53747d5d7ddd3c64444180643eb51b6142","tid":1482714,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"遇雨則吉，下雨代表陰陽調和，事情有結果，因此遇雨則吉。《象》曰：「遇雨之吉，群疑亡也。」上九爻裡，遇到許多奇奇怪怪的事情，讓人心中困惑不解，疑雲滿天。遇雨，又代表事情明朗，所有的疑惑一下子全都解開了，所以為吉。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"算罷啦，講呢啲"},{"pid":"adbd1113ceaa0dfb21d1c7e9b87237ca461f2d95","tid":1482714,"uid":9217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"你咁講係幫之前幾次警犬集會解釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ac6fc3bc37e5f4c989cf9abaeab44e45a759ac","tid":1482714,"uid":303018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T07:40:59.000Z","msg":"下雨為左淋息催淚彈<br />\n點講都得"},{"pid":"e295d1a70d65e22cbf002064d61cb8fc65715574","tid":1482714,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T08:02:24.000Z","msg":"唔似啦<br />\n睽卦是講人同人之疏離。意見不合。同床異夢。<br />\n但見今日之香港人團結一致， 似天火同人之象。<br />\n<br />\n香港。加油！"}]}